elements.title: one Bishop William
elements.contents: ... that in the 1260s one Bishop William moved from Agen to the Holy Land, while another Bishop William moved from the Holy Land to Agen, leaving some historians confused as to which was which?

elements.title: 1931 Salvadoran presidential election
